name: DGFamily Glass Box #2971
description:
The Glass Box is the gateway to the DGFamily. The Glass Box is transparent, yet you can’t see what it really holds. It could be anything: Black, Gold, or even the ultra rare Platinum. In time, you will be able to reveal its true nature…

Randomly reveal the Box's tier through an on-chain process at a future date. Glass Boxes default to Black Box benefits.

[View more details UNXD](https://drops.unxd.com/dgfamily/)

asset_contract.name: DGFamily Glass
asset_contract.description:
DGFamily Glass Boxes are redeemed for a tiered DGFamily Box during an on-chain reveal accessible in the coming weeks on UNXD.

DGFamily Boxes are the key to unlock access to the Dolce&Gabbana NFT universe – a world of digital, physical, and experiential benefits straight from the quintessentially Italian luxury brand, exclusively in partnership with UNXD. 

For more details, visit the [collection on UNXD](https://unxd.com/drops/dgfamily-glass-box/live)  and view the announcement on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/dolcegabbana/status/1495774561320767491)
